Goodman v. Dry Dock, E. B. & B. R. Co. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 8, 1890.)

Argued before Bookstaver, P. J., and Bischoff, J.

Thos. F. Wentworth, for plaintiff. I. M. Scribner, for defendant.

No opinion. Appeal dismissed, without costs to either party.
